        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         <em>
          Lithic is a modern, developer-first, card issuing and processing solution for innovative startups, fintech companies, and brands. They make issuing cards so much easier than you\xe2\x80\x99d expect.
         </em>
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         <em>
