         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkM1uhSAQhZ_msqsBFJAFi276GgaYuV5SBQNYY5--VJM2mZ_kTGZO5vO24pzyabZUKvktUz03NBGPsmCtmMleME8BDJN87MWgCZgB2ChGEsr0zIirDYupeUey7W4J3taQ4rVBKRfkZeDplPDIJes5ReeU0oj-2YNQICXo29fuEDB6NPiF-UwRyWJetW7l0b8_-EeL4zi6mKpLOcS586lJW0uf1i3tEZr45rP9PkkwnHJGR8YZF5LRjnUoB6nkqDgXAsaBcSolFVY7K8BrAY-BrjPvyu5Ktf6zXV9JNn9ubfz5sisu16D9ObW-7jHUc8Jo3YJwI6g3yQvKNGPE3AjDZOvFTymuG0Q53i83Rr3WnOkmNGdIbSv-m_4Aym6Ktg" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
          dove into
         </a>
         two of Tim Urban\xe2\x80\x99s on exponential growth. On Monday, I
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkM1uhSAQRp_msqsBBMQFi276GgZhVHIVDIw1vn2pJm3CTzKTmZPvOIswp3yZPRUkv8-A1w4mwllWQIRMjgJ5CN4wxXUrRU-8EZ5pqUkow5QBNhtWg_kAsh_jGpzFkOI9QSmXZDEKFHNeaDu6USjNJilaaH3LrZy866eHaw8fIDow8A35ShHIahbEvbzazxf_quc8zyYmHFMOcW5cqqW93oIWj_KxpfiGq5BgOOWMasYZl4rRhjWghOqU7jiX0mvBOFWKStuPVla-9C9Bt5k35RjrLveuqzeSzR-qtt-L3WC9GzXkUP_tiAGvAaIdV_BPfnw03kaGGSLkqtcPFm95Xcf7alDpJ28V1PY9Z30tVLJPdSr-Q38A-K6JiA" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
          went deep
         </a>
         on Eugene Wei\xe2\x80\x99s Status-as-a-Service. And today, we\xe2\x80\x99re turning to the King:
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkE1uxCAMhU8zLCMgQGDBopteI-LHTVATiMDpKLcvk6lUCYHMk_38vuAQllIve5SG5HXNeB1gMzzbBohQydmgzilaprgepTAkWhGZlpqkNn9VgN2lzWI9gRyn31JwmEq-OyjlkqxWuykICd5wCcKz4GT0I3DthBLcT_rt686YIAew8AP1KhnIZlfEoz3Gjwf_7Aef6bXREMreKw8Z17IfrWSSLKecUc0441IxOrABlFCT0hPnUkYtGKdKUemM7-7ByPgQdF_40E7f0IXv11BSbS7oS0156fL36nbYbqEHm_u7nznhNUN2foP4zoxvdDeFeYEMtSONs8Mb2DRx06mpv4wdymgMZ6Z_dOdYelf-N_0FDiSFCQ" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
          Ben Thompson
