        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Thompson has written so many of my favorite pieces in Stratechery. My
         <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkMGOhSAMRb_msRsDVRAWLGYzv2EQqpKnYADH-PfD08UkTZu0aW_vsabgHNOl95gL-aShXDvqgGdesRRM5MiYBu80EyBb3inidOeY5JL4PEwJcTN-1SUdSPZjXL01xcdwb1AKnCx6gtHwyVqwxvYISk0OulZx3nFEyftH1xzOY7Co8RfTFQOSVS-l7PnVfr_gp8Z5ns1u7PvaGhu32hjXOH8Khq-yxG3PMRCvgQKjkgEDLhhtWIOiE72QPQDnTnYMqBCUG1W_clZx9-roNkOTjzGXev5znCQdYhlj8mGu4_diNlzvQfU41LodwZdrwGDGFd1jvzwUbyDDjAFTpesGU252fQ-qAhTysVv5tEoBU7VRlV2sW-Ff9A8LF4i8" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
