          </a>
         </em>
         ).
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         I remember when I first heard that Amazon was buying Whole Foods in 2017. I was on the golf course, and I don\xe2\x80\x99t golf (it was for a friend\xe2\x80\x99s wedding), so it was particularly memorable. I remember that grocery stocks tanked, and that none of us were really sure what Amazon was doing. Ben Thompson did though.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         A year earlier, Thompson had written
         <em>
          <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkE2OwyAMhU9Tdq3A5S8LFrOZa0QE3AY1gQicmemcfmi6GMmypfdkPfsLnvBe6tNtpRF7tZGeG7qM321BIqxsb1jHFJ3QYK9KDiw6GYVVlqU23iri6tPiqO7Itn1aUvCUSj42OAfFZgdKy3CTVhkp4lVOBsLEDWqQxk5gzTvX7zFhDujwC-uzZGSLm4m2drp-nOCzV6Pazw1zty-hrF0BLnQfNOPZr_635DP5ny6w5ICD4FaA6OmCX8QFtdRGWwOgVLRSANeaKz9MXsUwqHiSfL3Dpe1TIx8erwRWXS40lZryvduP2a-4HEb_dOxz3XOi54jZTwvGNwR6szywjHfM-Do6jp4OgsbA0DFq-366U7oOA4ihCz05lr6V_0P_AA2diII" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
           The Amazon Tax
          </a>
          ,
         </em>
         detailing Amazon\xe2\x80\x99s overarching strategy across e-commerce (Amazon.com) and enterprise (AWS). When Amazon bought Whole Foods, he was ready. He called that they were running the same playbook that they\xe2\x80\x99d run with e-commerce, enterprise, and even logistics.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         I loved that piece because it distilled so much complexity down into an easy-to-understand framework\xe2\x80\xa6 which we will get to in a little bit.
        </p>
